      <title>杰富瑞聘请巴克莱资深银行家 Le Palud</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/jefferies-is-said-to-hire-veteran-barclays-banker-le-palud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 已聘请巴克莱银行投资银行工业业务全球主席蒂埃里·勒帕吕 (Thierry Le Palud)。]]></description>
